No. 851,

Misc.

Schack v. Florida et al. Petitioner pro se. Earl Fair doth, Attorney General of Florida, and George R. Georgieff, Assistant Attorney General, for respondents.

Motion for leave to file petition for writ of habeas corpus denied. Treating the papers submitted as &• petition for writ of certiorari, certiorari denied.

The following motions for leave to file petitions for writs of habeas corpus are denied.

Mr. Justice Douglas dissents.
